            "detailed_description": "Aegis is a 2D mech action shooter where you play as the last defender for a small settlement. Through exploring the frozen wasteland, you will gather vital resources to help your people build the Atmospheric Cleansing Unit, battle hostile scavengers, and find new parts to upgrade your ATEX Battlesuit. <br><br><br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/530520/extras/Key_Features.png?t=1475791246\" ><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li>Modular Mechs - Customize your ATEX Battlesuit to fit your playstyle.<br>    </li><li>Diversely Equipped Enemies - You're not the only one with the ability to customize.<br>    </li><li>Scavenging - Venture out to find resources and parts for the Atmospheric Cleansing Unit that is being constructed by your settlement.<br>    </li><li>Assault Bases - Find essential construction parts, rare items, and powerful weaponry by attacking enemy bases.<br>    </li><li>Armour Penetration System - Watch as low powered weaponry bounces off your thick armour harmlessly.<br>    </li><li>Diverse Item Selection - Many different items and weapons drastically change the performance of your ATEX Battlesuit.</li></ul><br>Soundtrack composed by Jim Hall.",
            "about_the_game": "Aegis is a 2D mech action shooter where you play as the last defender for a small settlement. Through exploring the frozen wasteland, you will gather vital resources to help your people build the Atmospheric Cleansing Unit, battle hostile scavengers, and find new parts to upgrade your ATEX Battlesuit. <br><br><br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/530520/extras/Key_Features.png?t=1475791246\" ><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li>Modular Mechs - Customize your ATEX Battlesuit to fit your playstyle.<br>    </li><li>Diversely Equipped Enemies - You're not the only one with the ability to customize.<br>    </li><li>Scavenging - Venture out to find resources and parts for the Atmospheric Cleansing Unit that is being constructed by your settlement.<br>    </li><li>Assault Bases - Find essential construction parts, rare items, and powerful weaponry by attacking enemy bases.<br>    </li><li>Armour Penetration System - Watch as low powered weaponry bounces off your thick armour harmlessly.<br>    </li><li>Diverse Item Selection - Many different items and weapons drastically change the performance of your ATEX Battlesuit.</li></ul><br>Soundtrack composed by Jim Hall.",
            "short_description": "The bombs have fallen, and the world has long since been covered in frost by a nuclear winter. It's up to you to build the machine that will return the earth to normal.",
            "supported_languages": "English<strong>*</strong><br><strong>*</strong>languages with full audio support",
            "reviews": "“Its tough and challenging, but not in a way that makes you think its impossible. I always end a game thinking &quot;next time, I'll try.....&quot;. I definitely recommend this game!”<br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://www.twitch.tv/martb64\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >MartB64</a><br><br>“A simple concept. Collect what you can to repair your base. What makes this game great is that there is no simple task. It is a challenge, and it is an amazing challenge. I expected to play this game for an hour or so. I can't count how many I've spent in it now.”<br>5/5 – <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCaj3dPiLPohxI4MQFVr2ooQ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >Bairdo</a><br><br>“Aegis is more punishing than you think! Combined with its kickass music, you'll want to keep playing this game for hours!”<br>5/5 – <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://www.alphavicely.com/?p=2020\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >AlphaVicely</a><br>",
